item.description:
theMOVE is rolling on to our next amazing farming/camping weekend, this time to the gorgeous Bay End Farm, at the head of the Cape in Buzzards Bay MA, home of Kofi Ingersoll and Erin Koh. Check out our photos from last year!

We'll have an amazing opportunity to connect with the farmers, work the land, and engage with others interested in learning how to reshape our food system. Most of our meals will be farm-fresh, some of which will be picked by our group, all of which will be prepared by our group.  We'll carpool from Boston on Friday evening and arrive back on Sunday evening. $80 trip fee ($70 for members) includes transit, meals, and camping arrangements (incl a tent if you need one).  Indoor beds are available for $10 additional per night.

We'd love for you to join us -- get all the info at getoutma.org/volunteer.
item.name: Cape Cod Farming/Camping Journey
